                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090412-17-victim161 t18090412-17-viclabel94"></join>; the prisoner worked for my mother, she <rs id="t18090412-17-deflabel95" type="occupation">takes in scouring and washing</rs>
